  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "This is the story of a man named John.  John was working in an ordinary
    company, sleeping in an ordinary apartment, and living an ordinary life. John
    was content with this normality, and would trade it with nothing else in the
    world. \n\tAnd then one day, Before going to sleep, John heard a loud, crashing
    sound. When he went to check his balcony, he came face to face with the body
    of an individual, dead. Before the horror sunk in, John noticed the world around
    him cracking, and now panic was added to the horror. The shine of an antique
    watch caught John's eyes, and he instinctively picked it up. When he clicked
    on the watch's button, the environment changed, as if he was in another century
    entirely! Only when he pressed it twice did he go back to his home...\n\tUsing
    this unknown artifact,  he now has to find the source of this mayhem and stop
    it, so that he can go back to his ordinary life!"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
